lead_paragraph: Karlie Samuelson made four 3-pointers and scored 21 points, Erica McCall had 19 points and six rebounds, and No. 13 Stanford beat Yale 102-44 on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: No. 13 Stanford Women Score 100-Plus for 1st Time Since 2011
